<plot>When his confidence scheme backfires, Rick finds himself in trouble -- the kind of trouble he can't run away from. He is forced by a Russian Mafia boss to play one hand of poker, with the prize being his girlfriend's life. Caught between the boss's bodyguard and hired gun, Rick has more than one job to pull off. Even if he wins at cards, can he regain the love of the woman he put in harm's way?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?320497</url></doc>
